# HTML Development Guidelines

## Styling Standards
- Use consistent color scheme: #003366 (dark blue), #6699CC (light blue), #E6EEF5 (light gray)
- Maintain 12px base font size with Arial font family
- Use CSS Grid for layouts, especially for icon grids and metadata sections
- Implement responsive design with mobile-first approach

## Component Structure
- Header sections with dark blue background (#003366)
- Metadata sections with light gray background (#E6EEF5)
- Interactive elements with hover states and transitions
- Status badges for visual indicators

## JavaScript Integration
- Use async/await for data loading
- Implement error handling with user-friendly messages
- Provide fallback data for offline viewing
- Use event delegation for dynamic content

## Accessibility
- Include proper alt text for images
- Use semantic HTML structure
- Ensure keyboard navigation support
- Maintain color contrast ratios